## **2. Flesh-xotiradagi boshqa fayllarni tekshirish**
Flesh-kartadagi fayllar **foydali maâ€™lumotlarni** oâ€˜z ichiga olishi mumkin.  

1ï¸âƒ£ **Flesh-xotira tarkibini tekshirish:**  
   ```
   ls -la /media/usb/
   ```
   yoki Windowsâ€™da:  
   ```
   dir E:\
   ```

2ï¸âƒ£ **Yashirin fayllarni topish:**  
   ```
   ls -la /media/usb/
   ```
   yoki  
   ```
   attrib -h -s /s /d E:\*
   ```

3ï¸âƒ£ **Flesh-xotirada zararli kod yoki backdoor bor-yoâ€˜qligini tekshirish:**  
   ```
   clamscan -r /media/usb/
   ```

4ï¸âƒ£ **Fayllarni metadata boâ€˜yicha tahlil qilish:**  
   ```
   exiftool /media/usb/*
   ```

