## **4. Himoyalanish choralarini koâ€˜rish (Blue Team)**
Agar **himoyalanish** vazifasi boâ€˜lsa, quyidagilarni bajarish kerak:  

ğŸš¨ **1. PFX faylni himoya qilish:**  
